        仕事をランダムに振り分ける際の<br>
        工数を削減
      </div>
      <%= link_to "新規登録", new_user_registration_path, class: "block text-center py-[17px] xl:py-7 w-[360px] xl:w-[480px] h-[60px] xl:h-[90px] bg-accent-register text-2xl xl:text-[32px] text-main-white font-medium rounded-full tracking-[0.2em] xl:tracking-[0.35em] !leading-none" %>
    </div>
    <div class="">
      <%= embedded_svg('fv-image', class: "md:w-[300px] md:h-[300px] xl:w-[500px] xl:h-[500px]") %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
